name: OpenNMN
description:
OpenNMN is Decentralized Biotech. The goal is to work together to create a biological method for producing the supplement Nicotinamide mononucleotide, also known as NMN. Biological methods will make it more accessible and allow the the means of production to be open-source and community owned.
